By Boluwatife Ezekiel Olaleye

Lionel Messi has told Barcelona team-mate and friend Paco Alcacer to begin looking for a new club in January.

Messi and Alcacer are close friends on and off the pitch but the Argentinian superstar apparently wants the striker to leave.

Spanish website Don Balon say Messi wants to see his pal thrive at a new club.

